Allelúia!
1 Salvátion and glóry and pówer to our Gód, Allelúia!
2 for his júdgments are trúe and júst. Allelúia (allelúia).

Allelúia!
5 Sing práise to our Gód, all yóu his sérvants, Allelúia!
you who féar him, smáll and gréat. Allelúia (allelúia).

Allelúia!
6 For the Lórd, our Gód the Almíghty réigns: Allelúia!
7 Let us rejóice and exúlt, and give him the glóry. Allelúia (allelúia).

Allelúia!
The márriage feast of the Lámb has cóme, Allelúia!
and his bríde has prepáred herself.  Allelúia (allelúia).
